extremeStpDomainTable.name: extremeStpDomainTable
extremeStpDomainTable.description: This table contains STP information per STP domain.

extremeStpDomainEntry.name: extremeStpDomainEntry
extremeStpDomainEntry.description: An entry in the extremeStpDomain Table.

extremeStpDomainStpdInstance.name: extremeStpDomainStpdInstance
extremeStpDomainStpdInstance.description: The unique identifier of this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainStpdName.name: extremeStpDomainStpdName
extremeStpDomainStpdName.description: The name associated with this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainStpEnabled.name: extremeStpDomainStpEnabled
extremeStpDomainStpEnabled.description: The Enabled/Disabled state of STP on this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainRstpEnabled.name: extremeStpDomainRstpEnabled
extremeStpDomainRstpEnabled.description: The Enabled/Disabled state of Rapid STP on this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainStpdTag.name: extremeStpDomainStpdTag
extremeStpDomainStpdTag.description: The StpdId of this STP domain which appears as the 802.1Q tag. Therefore, it must be the VLAN tag of one of the wholly-contained VLANs of this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainNumPorts.name: extremeStpDomainNumPorts
extremeStpDomainNumPorts.description: The number of physical ports belonging to this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainBridgeId.name: extremeStpDomainBridgeId
extremeStpDomainBridgeId.description: The bridge identifier of this bridge for this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainBridgePriority.name: extremeStpDomainBridgePriority
extremeStpDomainBridgePriority.description: The bridge priority of this bridge for this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainDesignatedRoot.name: extremeStpDomainDesignatedRoot
extremeStpDomainDesignatedRoot.description: The root bridge identifier for this STP domain as determined by the STP running on this bridge for this STP domain

extremeStpDomainRootPortIfIndex.name: extremeStpDomainRootPortIfIndex
extremeStpDomainRootPortIfIndex.description: The port ifIndex of the root port of this bridge for this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainRootCost.name: extremeStpDomainRootCost
extremeStpDomainRootCost.description: The cost of the path from this bridge to the root bridge of this STP domain

extremeStpDomainRRFailoverEnabled.name: extremeStpDomainRRFailoverEnabled
extremeStpDomainRRFailoverEnabled.description: The Enabled/Disabled state of Rapid Root Failover for this bridge on this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainMaxAge.name: extremeStpDomainMaxAge
extremeStpDomainMaxAge.description: The maximum allowable age, in units of hundredths of a second, of STP information learned by this bridge for this STP domain, after which it is discarded. This is the value currently being used by the bridge.

extremeStpDomainHelloTime.name: extremeStpDomainHelloTime
extremeStpDomainHelloTime.description: The time, in hundredths of a second, between successive transmissions of Configuration BPDUs when this bridge is(or is trying to become) the root bridge for this STP domain. This is the value currently being used by this bridge.

extremeStpDomainForwardDelay.name: extremeStpDomainForwardDelay
extremeStpDomainForwardDelay.description: The forward delay time, in hundredths of a second, currently being used by this bridge on this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainBridgeMaxAge.name: extremeStpDomainBridgeMaxAge
extremeStpDomainBridgeMaxAge.description: This is the value of MaxAge used by all other bridges in this STP domain when this bridge is the root bridge.

extremeStpDomainBridgeHelloTime.name: extremeStpDomainBridgeHelloTime
extremeStpDomainBridgeHelloTime.description: This is the value of HelloTime used by all other bridges in this STP domain when this bridge is the root bridge.

extremeStpDomainBridgeForwardDelay.name: extremeStpDomainBridgeForwardDelay
extremeStpDomainBridgeForwardDelay.description: This is the value of ForwardDelay used by all other bridges in this STP domain when this bridge is the root bridge.

extremeStpDomainHoldTime.name: extremeStpDomainHoldTime
extremeStpDomainHoldTime.description: This is the Hold Time, in hundredths of a second, for this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainTopChanges.name: extremeStpDomainTopChanges
extremeStpDomainTopChanges.description: The number of topology changes detected by this bridge for this STP domain since the management entity was initialized or reset.

extremeStpDomainTimeSinceTopologyChange.name: extremeStpDomainTimeSinceTopologyChange
extremeStpDomainTimeSinceTopologyChange.description: The time, in hundredths of a second, since a topology change was last detected by this bridge for this STP domain.

extremeStpDomainRowStatus.name: extremeStpDomainRowStatus
extremeStpDomainRowStatus.description: The status of this entry, as per standard RowStatus conventions.

extremeStpPortTable.name: extremeStpPortTable
extremeStpPortTable.description: This table contains port-specific information per STP domain.

extremeStpPortEntry.name: extremeStpPortEntry
extremeStpPortEntry.description: An entry in the extremeStpPort table.

extremeStpPortPortIfIndex.name: extremeStpPortPortIfIndex
extremeStpPortPortIfIndex.description: The ifIndex of the physical port for which this entry contains STP information.

extremeStpPortStpEnabled.name: extremeStpPortStpEnabled
extremeStpPortStpEnabled.description: The enabled/disabled state of this STP instance on this port.

extremeStpPortPortMode.name: extremeStpPortPortMode
extremeStpPortPortMode.description: The port mode of this port in this STP domain.

extremeStpPortPortState.name: extremeStpPortPortState
extremeStpPortPortState.description: The port state of this port in this STP domain.

extremeStpPortPortPriority.name: extremeStpPortPortPriority
extremeStpPortPortPriority.description: The port priority of this port in this STP domain.

extremeStpPortPortId.name: extremeStpPortPortId
extremeStpPortPortId.description: The port identifier of this port in this STP domain.

extremeStpPortPathCost.name: extremeStpPortPathCost
extremeStpPortPathCost.description: The path cost of this port for this STP domain.

extremeStpPortDesignatedCost.name: extremeStpPortDesignatedCost
extremeStpPortDesignatedCost.description: The path cost, for this STP domain, of the Designated Port of the segment connected to this port.

extremeStpPortDesignatedRoot.name: extremeStpPortDesignatedRoot
extremeStpPortDesignatedRoot.description: The root bridge identifier, for this STP domain, that is sent in the Configuration BPDUs transmitted by the Designated Bridge for the segment to which this port is attached.

extremeStpPortDesignatedBridge.name: extremeStpPortDesignatedBridge
extremeStpPortDesignatedBridge.description: The bridge identifier for the bridge considered to be the Designated Bridge, in this STP domain, for the segment connected to this port.

extremeStpPortDesignatedPort.name: extremeStpPortDesignatedPort
extremeStpPortDesignatedPort.description: The port identifier of the Designated Port on this port's segment, for this STP domain.

extremeStpPortRowStatus.name: extremeStpPortRowStatus
extremeStpPortRowStatus.description: The status of this entry, as per standard RowStatus conventions.

extremeStpVlanPortTable.name: extremeStpVlanPortTable
extremeStpVlanPortTable.description: This table contains information of the ports belonging to a STP domain on a per VLAN basis.

extremeStpVlanPortEntry.name: extremeStpVlanPortEntry
extremeStpVlanPortEntry.description: An entry in the extremeStpVlanPort table.

extremeStpVlanPortPortMask.name: extremeStpVlanPortPortMask
extremeStpVlanPortPortMask.description: The list of ports in this STP domain and in this VLAN.

extremeStpVlanPortRowStatus.name: extremeStpVlanPortRowStatus
extremeStpVlanPortRowStatus.description: The status of this entry, as per standard RowStatus conventions.

extremeStpEdgePortBlocked.name: extremeStpEdgePortBlocked
extremeStpEdgePortBlocked.description: The extremeStpEdgePortBlocked notification is generated when the STP's edge port is Blocked due to the misconfiguration
